                    "Enable developer self-service and build golden paths so that developers get stuff done. Reduce cognitive load on developers without abstracting away context and underlying technologies. Following best practices, we treat platforms as a product and build it based on user research and continuously improve it.",
                icon: "tabler:square-number-2"
            },
            {
                title: "Hybrid Cloud / Multi Cloud",
                description:
                    "For most enterprises hybrid cloud is inevitable, so you better have a good plan for how to make the best use of it. Split worksloads across different clouds or on-premises environments in an efficient and meaningful way and ensure security and compliance across all environments.",
                icon: "tabler:square-number-3"
            },
            {
                title: "AI & IoT Platfrom ",
                description: `Integrate artificial intelligence and the Internet of Things into a unified platform for real-time data analytics and actionable insights. This platform leverages AI's predictive power and IoT's sensor networks to enhance operational efficiency, personalize experiences, and proactively manage maintenance, boosting reliability and sustainability.`,
                icon: "tabler:square-number-4"
            }
        ]}
